    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! If you\u2019ve been searching for a car that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor, you\u2019ve found it! This beauty is in absolute mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it truly shows. Not a scratch or a smudge in sight, and the interior still has that fresh feel. It drives like an absolute dream and honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see it go, but it\u2019s ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
