    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a showroom-grade E92 M3, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving masterpiece delivers 414 hp with an 8,400 RPM redline, channeled through a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and zero bushing deflection. Meticulously maintained with documented rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, protected by a multi-stage ceramic coating. This is a collector-tier example with no mechanical compromises, featuring original forged alloy wheels and a pristine interior with no bolster wear.",
